reviewText: Such a wonderful cast that set a lot young Korean actors careers forward in the K-drama world. Its got one of the best bromances with so many twist and turns. It would be great to see a reunion show, but I don't see that happening.
Thank you so much. The package came undamaged and shipped quickly.
I loved the drama.  The dvd quality and English subs were good.  I didn't have any trouble with this dvd set.  I'm glad I bought it.
